# tinypets

Minimal JS interface to an image classifer deployed in Hugging Face Spaces - [Dog vs. Cat Classifier](https://huggingface.co/spaces/prasanthntu/dog-vs-cat-classifier). For full screen version, refer this [link](https://prasanthntu-dog-vs-cat-classifier.hf.space/)

## Curl examples
### Example 1: Dog
<img src="dog.jpg" alt="dog.jpg" width="128">

<details>
    <summary> To test out image classifier API, try out the below curl command </summary>

```bash
curl -X POST https://prasanthntu-dog-vs-cat-classifier.hf.space/api/predict/ -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"data": ["data:image/jpeg;base64,"]}'
```
</details>

and the response might look something like this.
